<div class="mb-4">
  <h1 class="h2">管理者ダッシュボード</h1>
  <p class="text-muted">システムの稼働状況と管理項目を確認できます。</p>
</div>

<div class="row g-4">
  <div class="col-md-3">
    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-primary bg-opacity-10 p-3 rounded text-primary me-3">
            <i class="bi bi-box-seam fs-4"></i>
          </div>
          <h5 class="card-title mb-0">商品管理</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="card-text text-muted small">商品の追加、編集、在庫補填、価格変更を行えます。</p>
        <%= link_to "一覧を見る", admin_items_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm w-100" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-3">
    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-success bg-opacity-10 p-3 rounded text-success me-3">
            <i class="bi bi-people fs-4"></i>
          </div>
          <h5 class="card-title mb-0">ユーザー管理</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="card-text text-muted small">利用者の学生情報管理やバランス確認が行えます。</p>
        <%= link_to "一覧を見る", admin_users_path, class: "btn btn-outline-success btn-sm w-100" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-3">
    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-info bg-opacity-10 p-3 rounded text-info me-3">
            <i class="bi bi-cart-check fs-4"></i>
          </div>
          <h5 class="card-title mb-0">購入履歴</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="card-text text-muted small">すべてのユーザーの購入ログを確認できます。</p>
        <%= link_to "履歴を見る", admin_purchase_histories_path, class: "btn btn-outline-info btn-sm w-100" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-3">
    <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-warning bg-opacity-10 p-3 rounded text-warning me-3">
            <i class="bi bi-cash-coin fs-4"></i>
          </div>
          <h5 class="card-title mb-0">チャージ履歴</h5>
        </div>
        <p class="card-text text-muted small">残高チャージの履歴と金額を確認できます。</p>
        <%= link_to "履歴を見る", admin_balance_histories_path, class: "btn btn-outline-warning btn-sm w-100" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
